#id=1
#text=I needed to go on my weekly grocery shopping trip last weekend .
#id=2
#text=So , I went to my fridge and started to make a list of the cold items that I would need .
#id=3
#text=Then , I checked out my cabinet to be sure that I picked up a few canned goods that I needed as well .
#id=4
#text=I checked through my coupons and took the ones that I needed .
#id=5
#text=I grabbed my wallet , helmet , sunglasses , and my insulated backpack and went outside to get on my bike .
#id=6
#text=After going through traffic , I arrived at the store and parked my bike .
#id=7
#text=I went into the store and grabbed one of the smaller carts , since I would not need to get too many things this trip .
#id=8
#text=I put my backpack and helmet in the cart and went inside .
#id=9
#text=I just needed some cream , milk , eggs , sausage , cheese , and some veggies .
#text=I dodged around other shoppers and headed towards the veggies .
#text=Salad blends were on sale , so I picked some up .
#text=I also grabbed a nice head of broccoli as well .
#text=Then I went to the refrigerated section and selected my meats and things , being sure to check for discounted meats .
#text=My list was all checked off so I went to the self-checkout to pay .
#text=I scanned my items , ran my coupons , and paid .
#text=I loaded my items into my backpack and put both it and my helmet on and left the store .
